  "title": "Marketing Assistant (West / 5 days)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Help bring our marketing campaigns to life across digital, print, and retail touchpoints.</li>\n  <li>Get hands-on with organizing store promotions, launches, and brand events.</li>\n  <li>Partner with sales and product teams to make sure our marketing supports key business goals.</li>\n  <li>Write and design content for social media, newsletters, websites—you name it!</li>\n  <li>Keep an eye on the market and our competitors to spot the next big trend.</li>\n  <li>Review campaign performance and help us understand what’s working (and what’s not).</li>\n  <li>Take care of marketing stock and samples—making sure everything gets where it needs to be.</li>\n  <li>Work with agencies, designers, and media partners to bring our ideas to life.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Who We’re Looking For:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>You have a diploma or degree in Marketing, Business, Communications, or something similar.</li>\n  <li>You’ve got 1–2 years of experience under your belt (bonus points if it's in marketing!).</li>\n  <li>You’re genuinely curious about consumer products and home appliances.</li>\n  <li>You’re familiar with tools like Meta Ads, Google Analytics, Mailchimp, and Canva.</li>\n  <li>You’re a confident communicator with a knack for writing.</li>\n  <li>You’re super organized and can juggle multiple projects at once.</li>\n  <li>You love learning and enjoy being part of a team.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No. 20C0270</p>",
